The bill passes with our support! The <span style="color: #cbc48a;">SNP</span> faced its biggest rebelion since it took government and the <span style="color: #3072b5;">Tories</span> fiercely opposed the bill, While <span style="color: #50bd47;">Scottish Labour</span> saw only a minor revolt for our support of the bill. Our image has improved with the transgender community and our left flank.

